      "characters_present": [
        "曹操",
        "王升"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王升上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王升",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领了一句话，千金不敢移。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王升",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在下王升的便是。我等奉太爷之命，画影图形捉拿刺客曹操。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王升",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计们，将图形挂起来。有人出入须要盘查明白。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（曹操上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "远望这中牟县城池一座，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且喜得上钩鱼逃出网罗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺这里忙加鞭城池经过"
        },
        {
          "character": "王升",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿曹操！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "耳边厢又听得有人拿我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住。耳听城门之下喊叫“捉拿曹操”，俺不是逃生，反是送死，待俺转回；"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀叱呸！大丈夫只有向前，哪有退后之理，待俺闯进城去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王升",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "作什么的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "进城去的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王升",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "进不得城了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何进不得城了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王升",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只因日前董太师行文，叫各府州县画影图形，捉拿刺客曹操。有腰牌放你进去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你拿曹操与俺什么相干？俺是卖绸缎的客人，有什么腰牌？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王升",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "没有腰牌，要拿你去见我家太爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你家太爷姓甚名谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王升",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我家太爷姓陈名宫，字公台。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少待。久闻陈宫素有贤名，我不免趁此机会，前去见了陈宫，用言语打动于他，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "管叫他弃职而逃，会合天下诸侯，共灭董卓，方遂吾愿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！把城的儿郎，俺便是曹操。见了你家太爷，难道他有斩人剑，将俺斩了不"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "成？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王升",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既是曹操，带上刑具。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这刑具不带也罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王升",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朝廷的王法。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要带，拿过来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我本待刺董卓与国除祸，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一似抢食鱼自入网罗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见陈宫我和他自有话说。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（曹操、王升同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "王升→曹操",
          "turns": 9
        },
        {
          "edge": "曹操→王升",
          "turns": 8
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 6,
          "念": 1,
          "唱": 2,
          "白": 15
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.111,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      },
      "scene_feature": [
        0.111,
